# 📇 JulioCard

Digital business card built with SwiftUI.

A simple iOS project created to practice layout, reusable components, custom fonts and asset handling.

---

## 📱 Preview

<p align="center">
  <img src="preview/JulioCard.png" width="300">
</p>

---

## 🚀 Features

- Custom profile layout using ZStack and VStack
- Reusable `InfoView` component
- Enum-based icon handling (system + asset)
- Custom font integration
- Clean and structured SwiftUI code

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Swift
- SwiftUI
- SF Symbols
- Custom Assets
- iOS 16+

---

## 📚 What I Practiced

- SwiftUI layout system
- Component extraction
- View composition
- Enum for UI abstraction
- Asset vs System images handling

